➪ my wish for you is to become hope; people need that....
caption:
films watched in 2018;

the amazing spider-man 2 (2014) | dir. marc webb

➪ my wish for you is to become hope; people need that. and even if we fail, what better way is there to live? as we look around here today, at all of the people who helped make us who we are, i know it feels like we’re saying goodbye, but we will carry a piece of each other into everything that we do next, to remind us of who we are, and of who we’re meant to be.

tags: clint barton is truly my number one
summary:
Clint in the vent using an ominous voice: Peter...PeTeR....PETER!
Peter, falling out of bed: Hello?
Clint: It is I...your...
body:
Clint in the vent using an ominous voice: Peter…PeTeR….PETER!


Peter, falling out of bed: Hello?


Clint: It is I…your guardian angel…Kyle.


Peter confused and horrified: What the FUCK Kyle? What kind of name is that for a guardian angel?


Clint: the kind that will totally kick your ass if you ever touch Clint Barton’s Cheerios ever again.


Peter now horrified: how…how did you know…


Clint still in the vent with the voice: I see everything you do…I also know what you did last summer…


Peter screaming loudly, running out of his room: MR STARK HELP ME KYLE KNOWS WHAT I DID!


…..


Tony still half asleep and annoyed: Clint get the fuck out of the vents.
